summary: I think my least favorite thing is when kaylors say people who disagree with them are homophobic. That’s the biggest myth in the...
question: I think my least favorite thing is when kaylors say people who disagree with them are homophobic. That’s the biggest myth in the whole fucking fandom. There are lots of Swifties who are not only not homophobic but open to or even pretty sure of the idea Taylor isn’t 100% straight. It’s other things kaylors do or say that makes them uncomfortable saying they’re kaylors, although I think a lot of the problem comes from just a few bullies/trolls (obv not you, you’re just the one doing asks rn)
answer:
There you go anon!

I’m super open to everyone’s opinion and I really encourage it. The last anon’s ask was okay until he (or she) dropped the “Kaylors are creepy” line. It’s one thing to have a different opinion, but it’s another one to just attack people about it. Hence the “homophobic” use. 

We just need to stay in our lane and be respectful with each other. There’s no need for insults. It’s just childish.

summary: And yet Joe Alwyn has been to several of Taylor's new shows and they don't publicize it because people would stalk him too. It's...
question: And yet Joe Alwyn has been to several of Taylor's new shows and they don't publicize it because people would stalk him too. It's almost like Taylor doesn't want people to harass her partners because that's all they do the moment they think she's with someone. Wow. Go figure. Meanwhile, Karlie has been MIA for a long time. Kaylors are creepy. Shipping REAL PEOPLE is creepy. Don't do it do striaghts and don't do it to lgbtq people either.
answer:
Hey anon, thank you for your opinion.

Every time Joe was @ taylors show, it was all over social media. So i’m not understanding why you say that they don’t publicize it? They literally put him right in the middle of thousands of swifties: that’s publicity enough. If they really wanted to keep it a secret, they would have put him at the same place as Adele when she went to the show: if it wasn’t for Taylor’s pic, no one knew she was there. That’s how you keep a secret. (just like Karlie in Pasadena… ahem…)

And there’s a difference between shipping and supporting. 

Please, don’t say that Kaylors are creepy. That’s just homophobic.

summary: Hello Taylor!!! I’m a Swiftie who is almost 17 years old,named Ceyda and always have been your side. Now I’m looking back and...
body:
Hello Taylor!!!

I’m a Swiftie who is almost 17 years old,named Ceyda and always have been your side. Now I’m looking back and saying to myself,choosing you as a role model was the most right decision I made in my life. You are always there for me even when you don’t have any idea about it :) but in every step I took I felt you by my side. I learnt a lot of things from you and apply these to life.I grew up with you and that makes me feel so great about growing up together and learning lessons together from life.I mean when I first saw you I was a little girl who doesn’t even know what she’s gonna do with her life but now I’m passing to senior year of high school.Scary.But now I know what I’m gonna do, I’ll just focus on the work(I have so so much important exam for passing to university this year) and I don’t let those people sidetrack me, someday when I get where I’m going, I will look around and I will know,it was me and the people who love me, who put me there.Thanks for teaching me how to feel myself free and confident about my ideas. And also you’re very strong woman and I’m so happy that you found your happiness with your real friends and your baby.You deserve every nice thing in this world. I adore you Taylor, you can’t imagine how big and endless my love and support for you. I want to meet you some day and hug you so so tight. Wish I could go to the Rep Tour but I can’t afford it and you’re not coming to my country, Turkey, but that’s okay ‘cause distance isn’t hurdle for us, you should know I’m gonna be with you whatever happens.I can’t put my feeling for you into words but all I can say is I love you,I love you, I love you.

love you to the moon and back

@taylorswift

I learnt a lot of things from you and apply these to life.I grew up with you and that makes me feel so great about growing up together and learning lessons together from life.I mean when I first saw you I was a little girl who doesn’t even know what she’s gonna do with her life but now I’m passing to senior year of high school.Scary.But now I know what I’m gonna do, I’ll just focus on the work(I have so so much important exam for passing to university this year) and I don’t let those people sidetrack me, someday when I get where I’m going, I will look around and I will know,it was me and the people who love me, who put me there.Thanks for teaching me how to feel myself free and confident about my ideas. And also you’re very strong woman and I’m so happy that you found your happiness with your real friends and your baby.You deserve every nice thing in this world. I adore you Taylor, you can’t imagine how big and endless my love and support for you. I want to meet you some day and hug you so so tight. Wish I could go to the Rep Tour but I can’t afford it and you’re not coming to my country, Turkey, but that’s okay ‘cause distance isn’t hurdle for us, you should know I’m gonna be with you whatever happens.I can’t put my feeling for you into words but all I can say is I love you,I love you, I love you.

love you to the moon and back

@taylorswift

like i get GG coincided with the public estranging of taylor swift but that’s not an excuse for belittling the harassment of a woman in an industry either than your own liiiike 🙄
